{"tid":1444971,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警入黎睇一睇 講個事實你地聽","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:23.000Z","uid":105590,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4cb2fafb2dbc75ad91199177a6061b9e44dc5d","tid":1444971,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"而家你地冇架啦 無論點都好你地一定會俾人清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地最好就親而家打多啲香港人 射穿人隻眼 爆多啲頭 上網搵多啲sp約返警局抱屌 再除多啲女仔褲睇 帶女仔返警處強姦 非禮多啲人 玩多啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係之後你地就冇機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地用下個腦諗一諗 到最後運動結束你地將會企係既位置係點就明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由一開始612開槍到而家 邊啲黑警俾人照過起過底既都即將會被清算 唔理係革職 再過住一世受香港人紅眼既生活 定坐監都好 都一定會以某種形式被香港人清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40362e5539b66d373b65eb896e33481a788b9f94","tid":1444971,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"魔警入！"},{"pid":"749a8269db4abca30cb4bd8c9bc0e1a30fd06b54","tid":1444971,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"我一世都唔